for (i in 0:42){
  x<-read.table(paste(paste('rmsd_',i,sep=''),'.xvg',sep=''),skip=18,header=F)
  plot(x$V1/1000,x$V2*10,type='l',ylim=c(0,25),xlab='time (ns)',ylab='RMSD (\u212b)',main=paste('replica', i))
  lines(c(0,220),c(2,2),type='l',lty=2)
}
